## Critical: slugifyCategory Differences

**Property & Dentists** replace `&` with `and`:
```
"Section 24 & Tax Relief" → "section-24-and-tax-relief"
"VAT & compliance" → "vat-and-compliance"
```

**Solicitors** strips `&` entirely:
```
"SRA Compliance & Trust Accounting" → "sra-compliance-trust-accounting"
"VAT & Compliance" → "vat-compliance"
```

**Medical** does not use category slugs in URLs (flat /blog/{slug}).

## Blog Post Front Matter

Markdown files in `{Site}/web/content/blog/*.md`:
```yaml
title: "Post Title"
slug: "post-slug"
canonical: "https://domain/blog/[category-slug/]slug"
metaTitle: "SEO Title | Brand"
metaDescription: "Description"
category: "Category Name"
date: "2026-04-01"
author: "Brand Editorial Team"
image: ""
faqs: [{q: "...", a: "..."}]
schema: "BlogPosting"
```

## Key Files Per Site

- `niche.config.json` — loaded by web via `src/config/niche-loader.ts` (import from `../../../niche.config.json`)
- `src/lib/blog.ts` — getAllPosts(), getPostBySlug(), slugifyCategory(), getCategorySlug()
- `src/lib/schema.ts` — buildBlogPostingJsonLd(), buildOgImageUrl() (Person author, dynamic OG images)
- `src/lib/local-business-schema.ts` — buildLocalBusinessJsonLd() for location pages
- `src/app/blog/[category]/[slug]/page.tsx` — blog post pages (Property/Dentists/Solicitors)
- `src/app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx` — blog post pages (Medical only)
- `src/app/blog/{category-slug}/page.tsx` — category hub pages (static)
- `src/app/locations/[slug]/page.tsx` — location pages with LocalBusiness schema
- `src/app/api/og/route.tsx` — dynamic OG image generation (edge runtime)
- `src/middleware.ts` — redirects for old flat /blog/{slug} URLs to /blog/{category}/{slug}

## Categories

**Property**: Section 24 & Tax Relief, Incorporation & Company Structures, Making Tax Digital (MTD), Capital Gains Tax, Portfolio Management, Property Accountant Services, Landlord Tax Essentials

**Dentists**: Practice accounting, Associate tax, Buying a practice, Practice finance, VAT & compliance

**Medical**: GP Tax & Accounts, GP Accountant Services, GP Practice Management, NHS Pension Planning, Locum Tax, Private Practice, Medical Expenses, Incorporation & Company Structures, Consultant Tax

**Solicitors**: SRA Compliance & Trust Accounting, Sole Practitioner Tax, Partnership & LLP Accounting, VAT & Compliance, Practice Finance & Cash Flow, Practice Succession & Sale, Structure & Incorporation

## Redirect Pattern

Property/Dentists/Solicitors have `permanentRedirect` logic in `[category]/[slug]/page.tsx`: if a slug exists under a different category than the URL, it 301-redirects to the correct URL. Dentists also has `middleware.ts` mapping old flat URLs to category URLs.

## Python Pipeline

Each site's `pipeline/` folder contains blog generation scripts. They use `config_supabase.py` which adds the repo root to `sys.path` to import `shared_supabase_config.py`. The `OUTPUT_MD_DIR` paths are relative to the script location, pointing to `../web/content/blog/`.

## Schema

All sites use Person author type: `"{Brand} Editorial Team"`. BlogPosting schema includes image (falls back to dynamic OG URL), absolute publisher logo, FAQ schema when faqs present. Location pages have LocalBusiness schema with absolute logo URL.
